#. <section class="sutta" id="sn17.23"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn17.23:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 17"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 17"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn17.23:0.2"
msgid "3. Tatiyavagga"
msgstr "3. The Third Chapter"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 23. Ekaputtakasutta → putto (pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn17.23:0.3"
msgid "23. Ekaputtakasutta"
msgstr "23. An Only Son"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pli2.236"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn17.23:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn17.23:1.2"
msgid "“Dāruṇo, bhikkhave, lābhasakkārasiloko … pe …"
msgstr "“Possessions, honor, and popularity are brutal …"

msgctxt "sn17.23:1.3"
msgid ""
"saddhā, bhikkhave, upāsikā ekaputtakaṃ piyaṃ manāpaṃ evaṃ sammā āyācamānā "
"āyāceyya:"
msgstr ""
"A faithful laywoman with a dear and beloved only son would rightly appeal to "
"him:"

msgctxt "sn17.23:1.4"
msgid "‘tādiso, tāta, bhavāhi yādiso citto ca gahapati hatthako ca āḷavako’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘My darling, please be like the householder Citta and Hatthaka of Aḷavī.’"

msgctxt "sn17.23:1.5"
msgid ""
"Esā, bhikkhave, tulā etaṃ pamāṇaṃ mama sāvakānaṃ upāsakānaṃ, yadidaṃ citto "
"ca gahapati hatthako ca āḷavako."
msgstr ""
"These are a standard and a measure for my male lay disciples, that is, the "
"householder Citta and Hatthaka of Aḷavī."

msgctxt "sn17.23:1.6"
msgid "Sace kho tvaṃ, tāta, agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajasi;"
msgstr "‘But my darling, if you go forth from the lay life to homelessness, "

msgctxt "sn17.23:1.7"
msgid "tādiso, tāta, bhavāhi yādisā sāriputtamoggallānāti."
msgstr "please be like Sāriputta and Moggallāna.’"

msgctxt "sn17.23:1.8"
msgid ""
"Esā, bhikkhave, tulā etaṃ pamāṇaṃ mama sāvakānaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ, yadidaṃ "
"sāriputtamoggalānā."
msgstr ""
"These are a standard and a measure for my monk disciples, that is, Sāriputta "
"and Moggallāna."

msgctxt "sn17.23:1.9"
msgid ""
"Mā ca kho tvaṃ, tāta, sekhaṃ appattamānasaṃ lābhasakkārasiloko anupāpuṇātūti."
msgstr ""
"‘And my darling, may you not come into possessions, honor, and popularity "
"while you’re still a trainee and haven’t achieved your heart’s desire.’"

msgctxt "sn17.23:1.10"
msgid ""
"Tañce, bhikkhave, bhikkhuṃ sekhaṃ appattamānasaṃ lābhasakkārasiloko "
"anupāpuṇāti, so tassa hoti antarāyāya."
msgstr ""
"If a trainee who hasn’t achieved their heart’s desire comes into "
"possessions, honor, and popularity it’s an obstacle for them."

msgctxt "sn17.23:1.11"
msgid "Evaṃ dāruṇo kho, bhikkhave, lābhasakkārasiloko … pe …"
msgstr "So brutal are possessions, honor, and popularity. …”"

msgctxt "sn17.23:1.12"
msgid "evañhi vo, bhikkhave, sikkhitabban”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn17.23:1.13"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
